lead_paragraph: Five-time defending gold medalist the United States unveiled a veteran-laden Olympic women's basketball team on Wednesday that will head to the Rio de Janeiro Summer Games seeking a sixth straight crown.

headline.print_headline: U.S. Sending Veteran Squad to Rio in Bid for Sixth Women's Basketball Gold
